{"type": "article", "id": 2633, "title": "Sony NWZ-WS613 运动型  Walkman", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-29T08:42:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232332yExkKams3X7w2TWg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t听到 Walkman 可能大家会想到单纯播放音乐的 MP3 ,随着产品功能走向多元化，Sony 推出 NWZ-WS613 运动型 NFC Walkman ，拥有防水防汗功能，带着它全天候做运动都没有问题，此外它还有一个指环无线遥控器，方便随时播放或更换曲目。值得一提的是，NWZ-WS613  特备有快速充电功能，只要充约 3 分钟就能使用大约 1 个小时，再充满电的情况下，可连续播放 8 小时。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232329niqsD7XES2vNu1or.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232330f3w9rAQNJe60cn7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232330lchFLgrVZkb2uwBi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323300RSLHYFmUu7DMWgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523233195MwNGJaDLi7VTkc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}